These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
7 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, pall-mall, siglo, aristoff, cain, havana, fonseca
 1. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the cain-smoker##5
 2. the aristoff-smoker is somewhere between the havana-smoker and the cain-smoker##7
 3. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere between the havana-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##7
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the siglo-smoker##5
 5. the fonseca-smoker is not to the left of the havana-smoker##8
 6. the pall-mall-smoker is in an odd position##4
 7. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the aristoff-smoker##3
 8. the havana-smoker is somewhere between the cain-smoker and the fonseca-smoker##7
 9. the siglo-smoker is not to the right of the aristoff-smoker##8
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Cigar   | cain | old-henry | pall-mall | siglo | aristoff | havana | fonseca |

