.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
There are 7 different favourite colors: aquamarine, green, pink, chestnut, blood-red, red, black
 1. the person who likes red is the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who likes pink is somewhere to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##5
 3. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes green##5
 4. the person who likes green is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes red is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 6. the person who likes chestnut is somewhere to the left of the person who likes green##5
 7. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 8. the person who likes red is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 9. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
10. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the person who likes aquamarine##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| Color   | chestnut | green | red | black | pink | aquamarine | blood-red |

