 2. the person who likes apricot is in an even position##4
 3. the person who likes black is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
 4. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 5. the person who likes coral is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
 6. the person who likes apricot is not to the right of the person who likes mauve##8
 7. the person who likes lavender is somewhere between the person who likes black and the person who likes turquise##7
 8. the person who likes mauve is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who likes mauve is not to the right of the person who likes lavender##8
10. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who likes orange##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
