.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: january, december, november, june, october, july, march
 1. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 2. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
 3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in december##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in june##7
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in march##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in june##8
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Birthday   | november | january | june | march | october | december | july |

